The fact that Trump is in office spouting White Christian Nationalist rhetoric and this is not mentioned as an issue in any way, shape, or form on the main website pages is a red flag to me as well, especially since a *lot* of Americans would say that racism and civil rights are significant issues in this country right now. Plus some of the proposals are already unpopular here and abroad (example: VAT is Not Popular in Britain and has disproportionally affected small businesses).
